snippet.title: Finding the Tomb of the Minecraft Mafia
snippet.description:
The Unstable SMP was once ruled by a team called the Invisible Mafia. Throughout their reign of terror, they amassed a fortune of items, which they hid in a place called the Tomb of the Mafia. This is Finding the Tomb of the Minecraft Mafia.

Like ParrotX2 and his Unstable SMP series, where he is escaping Paragon / Proton: Minecraft's Most Secure Prison, or got hunted by a Minecraft Player who doesn't exist. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or Lifesteal with Wemmbu, FlameFrags, or Spoke. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on.

People in this video: @TheobaldTheBird @Marlowww @RasplinYT @CoinMonkeExtras @Venpu @Willerhide herobanenair pro4d @TomLWSMC @qCxsh @NotBlueLeaf @Kibaxmc @nezoshoki 

Original Music: @tsynphonia 

This is a video on the Unstable Universe: a staged Minecraft server where ParrotX2, Wemmbu, Spoke, and FlameFrags tell stories in Minecraft.

A Minecraft video made by Parrot or ParrotX2 on other platforms! Enjoy!

snippet.title: IT: Welcome to Derry (2025) | Episode 5 Trailer | HBO Max
snippet.description:
#ITWelcomeToDerry 

🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
Return to the terrifying town of Derry in IT: Welcome to Derry as the legend of Pennywise unfolds like never before. In this chilling new HBO Max series from the Muschietti siblings and inspired by Stephen King’s iconic universe, dark secrets resurface and horror returns to haunt the next generation. Don’t miss the spine-tingling promos and final trailer for episodes 5 and 6—evil has come home.

The inspiration behind this video:
Step back into the terrifying world of Stephen King with Welcome to Derry, the chilling new prequel series to IT. In this Final Trailer, Pennywise's origins begin to surface in the haunting town of Derry, where nightmares are real and the shadows hide unspeakable horrors. Starring Jovan Adepo and Taylour Paige, and featuring creative direction by Andy Muschietti and Barbara Muschietti, this HBO Max Original Series dives deep into the twisted legacy of It. Fans of the IT movies and horror classics will finally return to where the terror began.

From HBO, HBO Max, and HBO Originals comes a fresh yet horrifying vision of the Stephen King universe. This spine-chilling series blends the iconic terror of Pennywise with a gripping narrative, delivering high-stakes suspense, emotional depth, and brutal scares. Welcome to Derry continues the tradition of acclaimed HBO Max Originals, joining titles like House of the Dragon and The Last of Us, and solidifying HBO Max as the home for the best horror and thriller series.

Stay tuned for more promos, including Welcome to Derry Episode 5 Promo and Welcome to Derry Episode 6 Promo. In today’s Hermitcraft S11 episode, we upgrade my starter base with a massive new Minecraft storage room and crafting area and it might be the strangest build I’ve ever created. Gem and I take Mumbo’s Happy Ghast, send it high into the sky, and have some fun with it. I also reveal my secret redstone cave hidden beneath the base.

This season’s base theme is fantasy-in-space: a sprawling spaceport and a massive redstone game project. The main base will be called Scar Worlds: The Movie.

I really hope you like the base story and ideas! See you in Hermitcraft episode 3!
